<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Apex Charity Cup</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #0f766e;
      --primary-dark: #0b5d57;
      --accent: #14b8a6;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --border: #dbe4ee;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
      --max: 1150px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(92%, var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,118,110,0.95), rgba(20,184,166,0.88)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574629810360-7efbbe195018?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      color: white;
      padding-bottom: 70px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 22px 0;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 22px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 60px 0 30px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 4.3rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: white;
      color: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .hero-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .hero-card li {
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }

    .hero-card li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 26px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 26px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .card h3, .card h4 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .impact-list,
    .feature-list,
    .sponsor-list {
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfeff, #f0fdfa);
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .stat {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 22px 18px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .sponsor-tier {
      border-top: 6px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .contact-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
      color: white;
    }

    .contact-box p,
    .contact-box li {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 24px 0 36px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero,
      .grid-2,
      .grid-3,
      .stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .nav-links {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">Apex Charity Cup</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#event">Event Info</a>
          <a href="#sponsors">Sponsors</a>
          <a href="#impact">Impact</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <div class="hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Compete. Contribute. Change Lives.</h1>
          <p>
            The Apex Charity Cup is a student-led two-day soccer tournament bringing together
            athletes, families, businesses, and the community to support St. Jude Children’s
            Research Hospital.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="#sponsors" class="btn btn-primary">Become a Sponsor</a>
            <a href="#event" class="btn btn-secondary">View Event Info</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <h3>Event Snapshot</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Date:</strong> April 25–26</li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> Apex Friendship High School</li>
            <li><strong>Hosted By:</strong> Play for Peace Foundation (501(c)(3))</li>
            <li><strong>Beneficiary:</strong> St. Jude Children’s Research Hospital</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">About the Event</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        The Apex Charity Cup is designed to combine competition, community, and service through soccer.
        The event brings together open-registration teams, high-level players, local businesses, and
        community supporters for a meaningful cause.
      </p>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What It Is</h3>
          <p>
            A two-day community soccer tournament featuring multiple brackets, community engagement,
            food vendors, and sponsor involvement. Organized by students, the event aims to use sports
            as a platform for service and impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card highlight">
          <h3>Why It Matters</h3>
          <ul class="impact-list">
            <li>Supports St. Jude Children’s Research Hospital</li>
            <li>Creates a student-led service initiative with real impact</li>
            <li>Brings athletes, families, and local businesses together</li>
            <li>Raises awareness through community participation and sponsorships</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="impact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Impact</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Every part of this event is built around making a difference. Proceeds support St. Jude, helping
        fund research and treatment for children facing life-threatening illnesses.
      </p>

      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>100%</strong>
          <span>of proceeds support the cause</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>2 Days</strong>
          <span>of competition and community engagement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>Student-Led</strong>
          <span>initiative driven by service and leadership</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>Local Reach</strong>
          <span>athletes, families, vendors, and sponsors</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="event">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Event Information</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        The tournament is structured to create a strong experience for players and attendees while
        maintaining a community-centered atmosphere.
      </p>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Open Bracket</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Ages 12+</li>
            <li>7v7 format</li>
            <li>15-minute halves</li>
            <li>Open-registration teams</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Elite Bracket</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>High school and club-level teams</li>
            <li>11v11 format</li>
            <li>Certified referees</li>
            <li>Competitive tournament environment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Community Features</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Food trucks and vendors</li>
            <li>Booth spaces for sponsors</li>
            <li>On-site promotion opportunities</li>
            <li>Family-friendly event atmosphere</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="sponsors">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Sponsorship Opportunities</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Sponsoring the Apex Charity Cup is a chance to support a meaningful cause while gaining visibility
        with athletes, families, and the broader community.
      </p>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card sponsor-tier">
          <h3>Why Get Involved?</h3>
          <ul class="sponsor-list">
            <li>Support St. Jude Children’s Research Hospital</li>
            <li>Increase brand visibility in the local community</li>
            <li>Engage directly with athletes, families, and students</li>
            <li>Show your commitment to service and community impact</li>
            <li>Receive social media and event-day recognition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card sponsor-tier">
          <h3>Sponsorship Levels</h3>
          <ul class="sponsor-list">
            <li><strong>Food Vendor:</strong> Free setup, vendor keeps profits</li>
            <li><strong>In-Kind Sponsor:</strong> Prize or product donations, promotion included</li>
            <li><strong>Direct Sponsor:</strong> Booth + social media promotion</li>
            <li><strong>Premium Sponsor:</strong> Expanded branding, booth, announcements, and more</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card contact-box" id="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color: white; margin-top: 0;">Get Involved</h2>
        <p>
          Interested in sponsoring, partnering, vending, or learning more about the event?
          We’d love to connect.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> divajain731@gmail.com<br>
          <strong>Organization:</strong> Apex Charity Cup / Play for Peace Foundation
        </p>
        <p>
          Reach out to learn more about sponsorship opportunities, event participation,
          or community partnerships.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      © 2026 Apex Charity Cup · Supporting St. Jude Children’s Research Hospital
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
